## 4. Design Comparison - PM Portfolio Standards

**Compared to Typical PM Portfolios:**

| Aspect | Your Site | Industry Standard | Gap |
|--------|-----------|-------------------|-----|
| Layout clarity | Good | Good | ✓ On par |
| Visual polish | Good | Very Good | Minor gap |
| Case study depth | Missing | Required | **Need to add** |
| Metrics/outcomes | Limited | Prominent | **Need to add** |
| Originality | Standard | Varies widely | Could improve |
| Mobile experience | Good | Good | ✓ On par |
| Load time | Unknown | <3s required | Test needed |

**Benchmark Examples to Reference:**
- Julie Zhou (simple, elegant, content-focused)
- Airbnb Design team pages (visual, metric-driven)
- Stripe product pages (clean, technical, outcome-focused)

**Your site positioning:** Professional and clean, but needs more substance (case studies, metrics) to stand out in competitive PM job market.

