### Navigation - Card to Experience Linking
- [ ] Add "Experience Examples" section below Availability
- [ ] Create 3 subsections (Discovery, Data/AI, Delivery)
- [ ] Add 2-3 examples per subsection with metrics
- [ ] Make profile cards clickable anchor links
- [ ] Implement smooth scroll behavior
- [ ] Add hover states + cursor pointer to cards
- [ ] Add scroll offset for fixed headers

### Visual Polish
- [ ] Add hover effects to all cards
- [ ] Subtle shadow lift on hover
- [ ] Cursor changes for interactive elements
- [ ] Entrance animations (subtle fade-in)
- [ ] Enhance hero background (gradient/texture)

### Content Additions
- [ ] Add key metrics to experience examples
- [ ] Format: "X% improvement in Y" or "Shipped in X months"
- [ ] Keep concise (1-2 sentences per example)
- [ ] Consider adding 1 brief testimonial

### Testing Required
- [ ] Mobile typography (real devices)
- [ ] Touch target sizes (min 44x44px)
- [ ] Smooth scroll on iOS Safari
- [ ] Performance (Lighthouse score)
- [ ] Cross-browser testing
```

